-06-11T21:56:14Z"}, "body": "A static file object should now its mime type.", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/issues/13/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/issues/13/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/issues/12", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/issues/12/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/issues/12/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/issues/12/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/kaj/ructe/pull/12", "id": 217052319, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MTEyNjI3NDI3", "number": 12, "title": "Integrate with sass", "user": {"login": "kaj", "id": 358770, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjM1ODc3MA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/358770?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj", "html_url": "https://github.com/kaj", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kaj/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2017-03-26T13:31:35Z", "updated_at": "2017-05-07T15:51:19Z", "closed_at": "2017-05-07T14:50:39Z", "author_association": "OWNER", "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/pulls/12", "html_url": "https://github.com/kaj/ructe/pull/12", "diff_url": "https://github.com/kaj/ructe/pull/12.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/kaj/ructe/pull/12.patch", "merged_at": "2017-05-07T14:50:39Z"}, "body": "Make it possible to add the css generated from a sass file directly as a static file, and to referense other static files from that sass file (and get the correct hashed named in the generated css).\r\n\r\nThe aim of this PR is to have something like `statics.add_sass_file(\"foo.sass\")` that automatically sassifies files and properly adds them.\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nlet mut statics = StaticFiles::new(&out_dir).unwrap();\r\nstatics.add_files(&base_dir.join(\"static\")).unwrap();\r\nstatics.add_sass_file(\"style.scss\".as_ref()).unwrap();\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe feature defines a sass function `static-name` that can be called with a source name of a static file to get the name including hash:\r\n\r\n```sass\r\nbody {\r\n    background: static_name(some.jpg);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/issues/12/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kaj/ructe/issues/12/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}]